formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
1) The actual cost has been given from unaudited account as on 30-06-2023.2) The sale value mentioned in annexure 3a regarding hotel unit amount receivable for hospitality project are provided only for the feasiblity of the project the sanction of the said hospitality project is mentioned in commencement letter and plan approved by appropriate authority. 3) As per sale agreement, two owners of land. The value of FSI has been divided between hotel and commercial project on 50:50 basis as per Hotel Policy 2016. 4) We have considered Rs.169500000/- which has been inured by Nirant Hospitality LLP who is co owner of the Project in land cost and the same amount has been show in estimated sales value as notional entry.
5) Estimated Cost of FSI is rs.47075527/- , however as per unaudited books of accounts cost for FSI till 30.11.2022 is rs.47154209/-
6) As per construction agreement for Hotel Unit, Firm has received rs.140900000/- as booking amount, hence the said unit has been shown now onwards booked under Annexure 3A.
